modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod adds craftable electric lights and other components. 24 craftable lights, numerous wireless relays and more.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds craftable [electric](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-electricity/) lights and other components.

* 24 craftable [lights](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-lights/)
* Numerous wireless relays and switches
* New Cube Generator and Fusion Generator

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/DelStryker/Delmod/tree/master/Delmod_Electronics)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11141-del-stryker-a17-modlet-collection/).
